(static) ACTION_BATTERY_ECG

The action value of event indicates the battery of ECG device.
The key and value will be as below:
KeyValue
actionECGProfileModule.ACTION_BATTERY_ECG("battery_ecg")
ECGProfileModule.BATTERY_ECG("battery")Battery status.
e.g. 90
message example:
{
    "battery": 90
}

(static) ERROR_DESCRIPTION_ECG

The Key of error description of ECG device.
Value range:

1:Electrode Loss.

2:Electrode Loss Recovery.

3:Electrode Loss Timeout.

4:SDCard Communication Error.

5:Collection Module Error.

6:Low Power.

7:Device Memory Full.

8:Disconnect.

9:Over Time.

10:Delete Error.

11:Error Data.

12:No Data.

13:Reset SDCard Error.

400:Parameter Error.

401:Firmware Version Is Not Supported.
